                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/1856</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-06-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 6, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Arrest of Congressmen yesterday created untenable position for us and I advised
                    Government to release them, which was done this morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
